115. (1) For the purpose of survey of liability of any person to tax under this Ordinance, an income tax authority may, notwithstanding anything contained in other provisions of this Ordinance but subject to such directions or instructions as the Board may issue in this behalf, enter any place or premises within the limits of its jurisdiction and-
